title: Episode 18: Walker Hayes
description:
On today's episode, Kailey sits down with family man and country music star, Walker Hayes. Walker shares the highs and lows of his journey of pursuing a career as an artist. He tells us more about the story behind his hit song, "Craig," that was inspiried by an incredible friend.
